name: Beffsbrowser
tagline: BeffsBrowser is a webbrowser project located at beffsbrowser.codeplex.com
body:
### Welcome  to the BeffsBrowser Site
This is mainly for the sourcecode of BeffsBrowser you can head over to (http://beffsbrowser.codeplex.com) for the setup file.
Soon The BeffsBrowser site will be back and you will be able to download as (alternative download locations) releases from Github or the main site 
### Easy to use 
BeffsBrowser is a simple easy to use Webbrowser!
